reviewText: Great Present for the guy who likes to fish catfish

This DVD is really full of information regarding catfish in is certain seasons and where to find them during each season. If you are trying to learn about catfish in habitats and their location patterns this DVD is for you.

This DVD has a lot to offer including showing you a look at red tail catfish in the amazon. They also show seasonal patterns with diagrams explaining where the fish are and they show a lot of catfish being pulled out of the water. Over all this DVD was nice but for veteran fisherman you probably already know everything in this DVD. Still worth checking out.
